ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T05:30:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>喺咪會貴過香港?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我見好多款香港都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n過多一，兩季香港就會有<br />\n你專門店睇？<br />\n果啲款好似唔係英國版來<br />\nMIJ的</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀, 我見日本賣就30,240 yen (HK$~2,150)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而英國官方網就145磅 (HK$~1,470)<br />\n所以唔知香港賣會幾錢呢...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋唔係MIJ來, MIJ個tag會多左JP字眼"},{"pid":"0434d1995e263f7ffd549bcd6d214b2fa051c9dd","tid":387724,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T05:49:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>喺咪會貴過香港?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我見好多款香港都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n過多一，兩季香港就會有<br />\n你專門店睇？<br />\n果啲款好似唔係英國版來<br />\nMIJ的</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀, 我見日本賣就30,240 yen (HK$~2,150)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而英國官方網就145磅 (HK$~1,470)<br />\n所以唔知香港賣會幾錢呢...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋唔係MIJ來, MIJ個tag會多左JP字眼</blockquote><br />\n我女朋友又係買左<br />\n4月果震<br />\n到八月係海港城見到有得賣 <br />\n不過價錢貴多一千<br />\n佢有啲MIJ  有啲日本限定<br />\n如果同款英磅平就緊係買英磅"},{"pid":"1cdd9242350b15e917ff9b25ecfc393f84107956","tid":387724,"uid":143962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T08:52:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>喺咪會貴過香港?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我見好多款香港都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/n